  <brief_title>CNAP Accuracy Dependent on Hemodynamic Variables</brief_title>
  <official_title>Accuracy of Continuous Non-invasive Arterial Pressure (CNAP) With Invasive Measurements Dependent on Cardiac Function, Vascular Resistance and Volume Status</official_title>
  <sponsors>
